metadata.name: Pomme de Pin #2
metadata.description:
This young boy is hidding his physical anomaly "Pectus carinatum" with a pincecone; 
and struggling a lot because of its deviation.

He said, "I am not as others mom, I am not normal. 
I'm shy to got to the swimming pool and take swimming courses because of this",  - and he lift up his t-shirt. 

I hug him gently and saying: "You are absolutely amazing, my boy. I love you".

We worked with him on confidence, talking about  mental fragility and the point of being distinctive and different. We are still talking about self-acceptance and self-care and love.

This work has been published in a PhotoVogue in February 2022.
